    "description": "<br>The demo version of EyeLove Survival!<br>Survive the onslaught of an endless horde of monsters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kill monsters, gather their eyes, improve yourself!</h2>In this roguelite survival game, all you can do is survive as long as you can. <br>Gather eyes for level up current run.<br>Gather credits in each run to buy upgrades and help the next survivor.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/462181ae5b7d2e77b13e5b00a75f3984.poster.avif?t=1768747763\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/462181ae5b7d2e77b13e5b00a75f3984.webm?t=1768747763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/462181ae5b7d2e77b13e5b00a75f3984.mp4?t=1768747763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Builds Every Run</h2>Select from a variety of upgrades to create a unique and overpowered builds every run. You can be a summoner-Drone Operator, for example, and destroy monsters with drones, or ranged sniper who use electrobullets to pierce enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/0a5c4dc1c9e6db8ed92eb2917d1bf8b7.poster.avif?t=1768747763\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/0a5c4dc1c9e6db8ed92eb2917d1bf8b7.webm?t=1768747763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/0a5c4dc1c9e6db8ed92eb2917d1bf8b7.mp4?t=1768747763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Select Your Hero</h2>Choose from a diverse selection of characters and weapons that offer a variety of gameplay experiences.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/4d865685f7cda8c9f404369da44e6584.poster.avif?t=1768747763\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/4d865685f7cda8c9f404369da44e6584.webm?t=1768747763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192860/extras/4d865685f7cda8c9f404369da44e6584.mp4?t=1768747763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 30 different upgrades too choose from for a unique experience every run!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wide cast of characters and their personalities, with more to come post-launch.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Casual quick 10-20 minute play sessions, for busy gamers.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Weapon, Orb and Item System helps you become stronger</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Future planned features</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cooperative Gameplay. Fight against hordes of enemies with friends</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>PvP Gameplay. Play against over players in Moba-style modes</li></ul>",
